msgctxt "2372dcb1-5029-433d-aa11-13e8e1ef4855"
msgid ""
"\"{name},\n"
"{br}I don't know where you are now. Are you even still alive?\n"
"I don't know what to do. But I am Queen and I must act accordingly.\n"
